      "text": "Un Dahwids bija to\nBrihdi Stiprumâ/ un tee Wilis-\nteri bij Betlemē Karra-Wihrus\nlikkuschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids fahze ee-\nkahrotees/ un fazzija: Kas dohē\nman Uhdeni dsert no tahs Ak-\nkas/ kas eeksch Betlemes Wahr-\ntim irr?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad lausahs tee trihs zaur\nto Wilisteru Lehgeri/ un finchle\nUhdeni no Betlemes Akkas/ kas\nWahrtis bija/ un nehme/ un at-\nneffe to pee Dahwida. Bet Dah-\nwids to ne gribbeja dsert/ bet is-\nlehje to preeksch ta KUNGA/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fazzija : Lai man\nDeews no ta pafarga/ ka es to\nbuhtu darrijs/-un scho Wihru Af-\nfini dsehris/ jo tee irr ar favas\nDsihwibas likstu to atneffuschi/\nun wiꞥſch ne gribbeja to dsert.\nScho darrija fchee trihs Warre-\nnee.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Abisajus Joaba Brah-\nlis bija arridsan par Wirfneeku\npahr trim/ un tas pazehle fa-\nwu Schkehpu/ un nokawe trihs-\nfints. Un tam bija arri Sla-\nwa starp trim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Starp teem trim bija\nwiꞥſch jo augsts ne ka tee diwi/\nun wiꞥſch bija teem par Wirfnee-\nku/ bet wiꞥſch ne panahze tohs\ntrihs ( pirmajus ).\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Benajus Jojada Dehls\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "weena stipra Wihra Dehls/ kas\nleelus Darbus darrijs no Kab-\nzeēles/ tas kawe diwi stiprus\nMoabitern Lauwas/ un nogahje\narridsan/ uu kawe weenu Lau-\nwu pascha Allā Sneega Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch nokawe arridsan\nweenu Egiptes Wihru/ weenu\ntahdu Wihru/ kas peezas Oh-\nlekts garsh bija/ un tam Egipte-\nram bija weens Schkehps Roh-\nkā/ ka weena Reestawa/ bet tchis\nnogahje pee ta ar weenu Sisli/\nun isrāhwe to Schkehpu no ta\nEgiptera Rohkas/ un nokawe to\nar winna pascha Schkehpu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Scho darrija Benajus\nJojada Dehls/ un schis bija fla-\nwehts starp trim Warreneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch bija tas aug-\nstakajs starp trihsdefiniteem/ bet\nwiꞥſch ne panahze tohs trihs\n(pirmajus). Un Dahwids ee-\nzehle to pahr tatweem Pils Karra-\nWihreem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta Karra-Spehka\nWarrenee bija: Asaēts/ Joaba\nBrahlis. Elanans/ Dodus un\nDehls no Betlemes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Saniots/ tas Aroriteris.\nFelez/ tas Peloniteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irus/ Ekesa Dehls tas\nTekōiteris. Abiesers/ tas Ar-\ntotiteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sibekajus/ tas Usatite-\nris. Ilajus/ tas Akōiteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Makarajus/ tas Neto-\nwatiteris. Geleds/ Baenus\nDehls/ tas Netowatiteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Itajus/Ribaja Dehls no\nHhhh\n"
